### Variáveis
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3001
@contentType = application/json

### Health check
# @name healthCheck
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Criar agendamento
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/appointments
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "paciente": "Lucas Freitas",
  "data": "2025-08-14T09:00:00",
  "procedimento": "Limpeza dental"
}

### Listar agendamentos
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/appointments

### Buscar agendamentos por ID
@appointmentId = {{createAppointment_response.body.id}}
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/appoinments/{{appointmentId}}

### Atualizar agendamento
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/appointments/{{appointmentId}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "procedimento": "Limpeza dental + aplicação de flúor"
}

### Deletar agendamento
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/appointments/{{appointmentId}}